{"tid":1176696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「雙非童」怨恨 香港：「根本 無福利 可以搶！」","createTime":"2019-05-29T11:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T12:04:52.000Z","uid":226548,"like":3,"dislike":251,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"620f5b798846bf317147dcea266ff7e67feda2f4","tid":1176696,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>「香港沒甚資源可以搶」</strong><br />\n<br />\n華仔（化名）不諱言，一直以來都是自食其力，「香港政府很多政策表面上講到會幫你，但其實幫不了太多，就好似我<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">申請過三年綜援，但綜援金額只勉強夠付房租</span></strong>，我若再搵工做，所賺的超出一定金額，又要扣綜援金，變相減低人自力更生的動力。最後我索性自己搵工做，不靠綜援。」他知道，部分香港人或會覺得雙非來港搶資源，「實際是否這個情況呢？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我也有交稅，也有盡香港人的公民責任。更何況，香港並沒有甚麼資源可以讓我搶。</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n今天的他，心中沒有所謂「怨恨」，「香港其實有很多熱心市民，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">曾經就有一位不知名人士，幫我交了一年租</span></strong>，我很感激他。」接下來的日子，他希望有機會與女朋友一同供樓，「其實雙非又好，單非又好，本地人也好，最後同樣要面對住屋問題&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"49d82ff256e9108c966a54092de9efba75e1ea97","tid":1176696,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:32:21.000Z","msg":"<ins><a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/935691/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F935691%2F&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LvBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=6afb4562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/935691/</a></ins>"},{"pid":"db61edc122e73eaa9a0b5c449c837cddaec3fb69","tid":1176696,"uid":66324,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"要去到拎綜援但又要交稅? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526eb11fc0eaa26bb730b9c02027a75bd4293d0a","tid":1176696,"uid":19552,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"綜援都要美稅? 賭波輸錢當交稅"},{"pid":"8e9cef35c0d5146b48c3d264f0a598561f9a8f62","tid":1176696,"uid":4